'''Death hollows''' were depressions of [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal's]] [[Korunnal Highland]] where volcanic gases could aggregate and produce [[Poison/Legends|toxic]] pockets deadly to animals. The gases stimulated plant growth, however, causing death hollows to become even more profuse with plant life than the rest of the surrounding jungle.

